Flamer
A '''flamer''' could refer to one of two types of people:

#A [[faggot|raging homosexual]]
#A [[troll]] or other user who engages in a [[flame war]] on the [[internets]]

'''Flamers''' are also used as a generic term for devices designed to cause fire at the least possible risk to the operator ( typically several feet away from them). It is currently Illegal to use Flamers(tool) on flamers(Anonymous) but many right thinking individuals are attempting to rectify this.

